						               													<description>From the publisher's website:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Night of Crime and Chaos in the Caribbean.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every night if a party in Margaritaland, the most exclusive tropical resort on the island!  While most choose this vacation destination to escape their troubles, for one individual it will mean the end of their travels altogether. Join the rich, the famous and the resort staff to decipher the clues and catch a culprit in the act of killing!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This mystery is formatted to be able to be run indoors or out!  Perfect for pool parties, summer BBQs, beach parties, you name it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The package includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     A Host Guide&amp;mdash; A complete how-to of throwing your party which includes directions on preparing the invitations, assigning characters and preparing for the party.&amp;#10;     A Schedule of the Night&amp;mdash; A step-by-step breakdown of how the night will go.&amp;#10;     An Introduction&amp;mdash; to be read to the guests upon arrival.&amp;#10;     Designed Invitations&amp;mdash; that you can customize with the details of your party.&amp;#10;     The Island Review&amp;mdash; to be sent with the invitations, it includes background information on the happenings in and around the island and the guests coming to the party.&amp;#10;     Character Sheets&amp;mdash; full descriptions of the characters, including costuming and acting tips.&amp;#10;     Character Objective Sheets &amp;mdash;this includes objectives for each character to try to achieve at each stage of the game in order to uncover evidence and find the murderer.&amp;#10;     Name Tags&amp;#10;     Fake Money&amp;mdash; to be distributed to guests and used in the party for scheming and bribery.&amp;#10;     Evidence &amp;mdash; more clues that will be presented towards the end of the night. This evidence will help your guests solve the mystery and find the murderer.&amp;#10;     Solution&amp;mdash; a detailed description of who the murderer is, why the murder happened and the clues that led to the outcome.&amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Who Dunnit&amp;rdquo; Cards&amp;mdash; to allow your guests to guess the murderer, along with vote for the most animated character and best outfit.&amp;#10;     Award Certificates&amp;mdash; to be awarded to the best costume, the most theatrical guest, the player with the most money at the end of the night and to each of the guests that solve the murder.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;THREE SEPARATE VERSIONS FORMATTED FOR UP TO 80 GUESTS!&amp;#10;10-15 GUESTS -- 15-20 GUESTS -- 20-80 GUESTS&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Home Page: http://www.nightofmystery.com/Murder_in_Margaritaland.php&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
